rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0001
rows.name:
I'm a wanderer, traveling
Alst as the wind takes me.

rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0002
rows.name:
The people of Hræsvelgr were kind
enough to let me stay awhile.

rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0003
rows.name:
Don't you think the markings
on Hræsvelgr's cave walls
are fascinating?

rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0004
rows.name:
I can't read them myself, but
I think they're some kind of
inscriptions from long ago.

rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0005
rows.name:
I've traveled all over,
and I can tell you they're
a pretty unusual sight.

rows.label: tlk45420141_01_tlk0006
rows.name:
There's a friend of mine in the
Superbian capital, name of Hassane,
who might be able to figure them out.
